ptolemy.data.expr

Class ParseTreeTypeInference

  • java.lang.Object
    • ptolemy.data.expr.AbstractParseTreeVisitor
      • ptolemy.data.expr.ParseTreeTypeInference
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParseTreeVisitor

    public class ParseTreeTypeInference
extends AbstractParseTreeVisitor
    This class visits parse trees and infers a type for each node in the parse tree. This type is stored in the parse tree.
    Since:
    Ptolemy II 2.1
    Author:
    Steve Neuendorffer
    See Also:
    ASTPtRootNode
    Pt.AcceptedRating:
    Yellow (neuendor)
    Pt.ProposedRating:
    Green (neuendor)
